00:00:48.515 --> 00:00:49.975 line:90%
It is not over yet.

00:01:02.529 --> 00:01:03.613 line:90%
Now…

00:01:06.283 --> 00:01:08.118 line:90%
let us make a pact.

00:01:10.954 --> 00:01:14.040 line:90%
I will give you half of my Yang energy.
In exchange…

00:01:16.501 --> 00:01:18.044 line:90%
help me.

00:02:09.721 --> 00:02:11.056 line:90%
Damn it.

00:02:49.678 --> 00:02:50.637 line:90%
At this rate,

00:02:51.471 --> 00:02:53.556 line:90%
your soul will be destroyed.

00:02:56.142 --> 00:02:58.019 line:90%
If you reveal your true self now,

00:02:59.813 --> 00:03:01.606 line:90%
I will grant you the chance to pass on.

00:03:44.899 --> 00:03:45.859 line:90%
No.

00:03:46.943 --> 00:03:48.486 line:90%
That is not what we agreed to.

00:03:50.196 --> 00:03:51.531 line:90%
If I lose all my Yang energy…

00:03:53.575 --> 00:03:54.701 line:90%
I will die.

00:05:17.659 --> 00:05:19.202 line:90%
I told you not to pull…

00:05:31.422 --> 00:05:36.344 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:05:42.725 --> 00:05:43.977 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:05:46.980 --> 00:05:48.731 line:90%
Prince Yeongan is safe.

00:05:49.816 --> 00:05:52.026 line:90%
You were the one who saved him,
were you not?

00:05:53.570 --> 00:05:56.239 line:90%
More importantly,
why did you pull the rope?

00:05:57.824 --> 00:05:59.617 line:90%
The bell suddenly stopped ringing.

00:05:59.701 --> 00:06:01.953 line:90%
I thought you might be in danger,
so I pulled it.

00:06:03.454 --> 00:06:04.372 line:90%
Did I interrupt?

00:06:04.455 --> 00:06:10.211 line:90%
I clearly told you not to pull that rope,
but you never listen.

00:06:10.295 --> 00:06:11.880 line:90%
Good grief.

00:06:12.672 --> 00:06:15.633 line:90%
Did you get rid of the pond spirit?

00:06:17.510 --> 00:06:19.929 line:90%
I merely drained a portion of its power.

00:06:21.306 --> 00:06:23.850 line:90%
Even so, it will not be able to move
for a while.

00:06:34.736 --> 00:06:35.737 line:90%
Why that look?

00:06:35.820 --> 00:06:36.779 line:90%
Well,

00:06:38.198 --> 00:06:42.493 line:90%
I regret taking you for nothing
but a layabout and a swindler.

00:06:43.912 --> 00:06:44.954 line:90%
I once thought

00:06:45.038 --> 00:06:49.167 line:90%
you were a heartless man
who cared little for human lives…

00:06:49.250 --> 00:06:50.084 line:90%
Goodness.

00:06:51.419 --> 00:06:52.629 line:90%
…and only for himself.

00:06:56.090 --> 00:06:59.802 line:90%
Well, that is not entirely wrong.
Yet it does not feel so…

00:07:01.304 --> 00:07:02.347 line:90%
In any case,

00:07:03.514 --> 00:07:06.684 line:90%
His Majesty will be grateful
that you saved Prince Yeongan.

00:07:08.019 --> 00:07:10.897 line:90%
Then would you ask your father
to let me leave the palace?

00:07:16.527 --> 00:07:17.904 line:90%
How did you find out?

00:07:19.530 --> 00:07:21.950 line:90%
-Since when?
-From the moment I first saw you.

00:07:23.326 --> 00:07:26.663 line:90%
I wondered who His Majesty
would send in secret,

00:07:26.746 --> 00:07:29.082 line:90%
but a court lady with delicate hands?
Impossible.

00:07:30.875 --> 00:07:32.126 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:07:34.045 --> 00:07:37.674 line:90%
-And you look exactly like the King.
-Huh?

00:07:37.757 --> 00:07:38.800 line:90%
The strong presence

00:07:39.717 --> 00:07:42.929 line:90%
and that stubborn look.

00:07:44.305 --> 00:07:47.308 line:90%
Wait, is that why you told me
to show my blood earlier?

00:07:48.643 --> 00:07:52.730 line:90%
You used me as bait, knowing the spirit
held a grudge against the royal bloodline?

00:07:52.814 --> 00:07:56.150 line:90%
I needed to distract the pond spirit.

00:07:56.234 --> 00:07:58.903 line:90%
At least His Majesty chose
the right person.

00:08:07.453 --> 00:08:08.788 line:90%
Speaking of which…

00:08:15.628 --> 00:08:18.381 line:90%
How about joining hands with me
in secret from His Majesty?

00:08:23.094 --> 00:08:23.928 line:90%
Here.

00:08:29.475 --> 00:08:35.356 line:90%
I can only stay here to watch you
while you resolve the pond spirit matter.

00:08:36.441 --> 00:08:37.358 line:90%
So

00:08:38.234 --> 00:08:40.820 line:90%
buy me time in the palace.

00:08:42.530 --> 00:08:44.490 line:90%
What do you plan to do meanwhile?

00:08:45.116 --> 00:08:46.743 line:90%
I am going to kill

00:08:47.327 --> 00:08:48.578 line:90%
someone in the palace.

00:08:49.871 --> 00:08:50.705 line:90%
<i>Your Majesty.</i>

00:08:51.289 --> 00:08:54.292 line:90%
A child who once served
the late Crown Prince

00:08:54.375 --> 00:08:56.878 line:90%
requested an audience with you.

00:09:00.840 --> 00:09:04.260 line:90%
He claims to know something

00:09:04.927 --> 00:09:06.888 line:90%
about the Crown Prince
and the pond spirit.

00:09:11.017 --> 00:09:12.310 line:90%
Let him in.

00:09:26.699 --> 00:09:27.617 line:90%
Very well.

00:09:28.117 --> 00:09:29.577 line:90%
Is there

00:09:30.995 --> 00:09:32.789 line:90%
something you must tell me?

00:10:06.823 --> 00:10:08.408 line:90%
You are young

00:10:10.451 --> 00:10:12.120 line:90%
yet courageous.

00:10:20.378 --> 00:10:21.712 line:90%
Yes, right here.

00:10:50.992 --> 00:10:54.203 line:90%
<i>Why should I join hands with you</i>
<i>in secret from His Majesty?</i>

00:10:55.204 --> 00:10:59.375 line:90%
Because those who learn secrets
of the palace cannot leave alive.

00:11:00.334 --> 00:11:04.672 line:90%
So if I help you,
you will let me leave the palace alive?

00:11:28.654 --> 00:11:30.865 line:90%
But how did you hear the bell?

00:11:34.243 --> 00:11:37.538 line:90%
I have abilities like yours.

00:12:13.407 --> 00:12:14.575 line:90%
Mother!

00:12:14.659 --> 00:12:16.077 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:12:17.203 --> 00:12:19.163 line:90%
Is there something inside?

00:12:20.122 --> 00:12:21.290 line:90%
Princess.

00:12:21.791 --> 00:12:24.460 line:90%
What do you think you are doing here?

00:12:26.128 --> 00:12:27.463 line:90%
<i>"The pond spirit."</i>

00:12:28.464 --> 00:12:31.425 line:90%
"The serpent's cast skin
killed the dragon's child."

00:12:32.218 --> 00:12:33.761 line:90%
Those were the words of the spirit

00:12:33.844 --> 00:12:36.305 line:90%
that was once trapped there
when I was a child.

00:12:36.389 --> 00:12:39.308 line:90%
The dragon's child means
the son of the King,

00:12:39.392 --> 00:12:42.770 line:90%
so the serpent's cast skin
must refer to the pond spirit.

00:12:42.853 --> 00:12:43.688 line:90%
What are you--

00:12:43.771 --> 00:12:45.815 line:90%
In any case,
looking into the salt storehouse

00:12:45.898 --> 00:12:48.109 line:90%
will tell us more about the pond spirit.

00:12:51.821 --> 00:12:54.365 line:90%
-Your reason for returning--
-None of your concern.

00:12:57.618 --> 00:13:00.621 line:90%
All you need to do
is look into the pond spirit.

00:13:01.122 --> 00:13:04.500 line:90%
So you were cast out of the palace
for hearing spirits.

00:13:05.418 --> 00:13:07.044 line:90%
You are a princess,

00:13:07.128 --> 00:13:09.046 line:90%
yet you have shamanic gifts.

00:13:10.131 --> 00:13:12.967 line:90%
What happened as a child
that you are able to hear spirits?

00:13:13.050 --> 00:13:17.471 line:90%
How were you raised
to twist the knife with every word?

00:13:19.348 --> 00:13:22.143 line:90%
You are overly sensitive about nothing.

00:13:22.226 --> 00:13:23.269 line:90%
Nothing?

00:13:27.273 --> 00:13:30.234 line:90%
Seeing that you do not know
how to consider others' feelings,

00:13:30.318 --> 00:13:32.236 line:90%
even your friends and family
must hate you.

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:34.947 line:90%
I have neither friends nor family.
I am an orphan.

00:13:37.950 --> 00:13:39.535 line:90%
And you are hardly one to talk.

00:13:40.161 --> 00:13:42.079 line:90%
Do you have any friends?

00:13:43.873 --> 00:13:46.334 line:90%
-Are all royalty born insufferable--
-Enough!

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:50.504 line:90%
Just check the salt storehouse
so you can catch the pond spirit.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:53.716 line:90%
Good grief.

00:13:54.467 --> 00:13:55.676 line:90%
Oh dear.

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:57.803 line:90%
This pond spirit…

00:13:59.388 --> 00:14:00.348 line:90%
Hold on.

00:14:04.226 --> 00:14:05.061 line:90%
No…

00:14:12.610 --> 00:14:14.820 line:90%
Do not tell me…

00:14:15.404 --> 00:14:17.323 line:90%
-Why are you going there?
-It cannot be.

00:14:17.406 --> 00:14:18.908 line:90%
-It cannot be.
-What?

00:14:19.533 --> 00:14:21.827 line:90%
-Wait.
-Did you find something there?

00:14:27.083 --> 00:14:28.709 line:90%
I was saving it for later.

00:14:32.588 --> 00:14:33.631 line:90%
-So it is here.
-What?

00:14:34.757 --> 00:14:35.966 line:90%
-A gwi-mae.
-A gwi-mae?

00:14:36.050 --> 00:14:37.593 line:90%
Must find out what it really is.

00:14:39.345 --> 00:14:40.888 line:90%
-Where did the rice cake…
-Wait.

00:14:40.971 --> 00:14:42.807 line:90%
-Why are you throwing--
-Quiet!

00:14:43.933 --> 00:14:46.185 line:90%
Just be quiet for a moment.

00:14:58.989 --> 00:15:01.117 line:90%
This is bad. No!

00:15:01.617 --> 00:15:03.035 line:90%
What is there?

00:15:05.746 --> 00:15:08.040 line:90%
-Look--
-We need to get out of here.

00:15:09.125 --> 00:15:10.251 line:90%
Let us go.

00:15:11.585 --> 00:15:13.295 line:90%
-Hurry!
-Wait.

00:15:13.963 --> 00:15:15.673 line:90%
We need to check!

00:15:23.222 --> 00:15:26.642 line:90%
You said it was a gwi-mae.
And that it is bound to a place.

00:15:27.143 --> 00:15:29.687 line:90%
-We should be fine.
-Hold on!

00:15:32.314 --> 00:15:35.025 line:90%
That one is called Ggeomeoksali.

00:15:35.109 --> 00:15:36.610 line:90%
It is no ordinary creature.

00:15:36.694 --> 00:15:39.613 line:90%
It attaches to the living, not places,
feeding on Yang energy.

00:15:39.697 --> 00:15:44.034 line:90%
-Yang energy?
-Those drained of it see terror and die.

00:15:45.661 --> 00:15:47.288 line:90%
It is a terrifying creature.

00:15:47.371 --> 00:15:48.330 line:90%
But…

00:15:50.291 --> 00:15:51.584 line:90%
I get it. Stop pushing me.

00:15:51.667 --> 00:15:52.626 line:90%
Then

00:15:53.961 --> 00:15:55.588 line:90%
let us go see your new quarters.

00:15:55.671 --> 00:15:58.758 line:90%
His Majesty reassigned them
for saving Prince Yeongan.

00:15:59.925 --> 00:16:01.719 line:90%
Why are you telling me this now?

00:16:03.012 --> 00:16:04.930 line:90%
-Well…
-Where is it?

00:16:07.099 --> 00:16:08.934 line:90%
That way. Over there.

00:16:09.977 --> 00:16:11.937 line:90%
Hurry. Quick!

00:16:12.438 --> 00:16:14.023 line:90%
I will walk myself.

00:16:17.860 --> 00:16:18.694 line:90%
Good grief.

00:16:19.403 --> 00:16:21.572 line:90%
I cannot believe this.

00:16:23.157 --> 00:16:25.576 line:90%
-Oh dear.
-What are you staring at?

00:16:25.659 --> 00:16:27.161 line:90%
I should not have trusted.

00:16:27.244 --> 00:16:28.996 line:90%
Good grief. Truly…

00:16:29.079 --> 00:16:31.457 line:90%
How do you like the room?

00:16:35.669 --> 00:16:38.088 line:90%
I just moved to the room across.

00:16:38.923 --> 00:16:39.924 line:90%
Goodness.

00:16:44.345 --> 00:16:45.763 line:90%
It followed us here.

00:16:47.848 --> 00:16:48.682 line:90%
What?

00:16:50.142 --> 00:16:51.352 line:90%
Ggeomeoksali.

00:16:51.435 --> 00:16:52.394 line:90%
What?

00:16:53.938 --> 00:16:55.064 line:90%
Ggeomeoksali.

00:16:59.985 --> 00:17:00.820 line:90%
No!

00:17:02.404 --> 00:17:04.448 line:90%
Goodness. It clings like a leech.

00:17:07.117 --> 00:17:08.828 line:90%
What is it now?

00:17:12.665 --> 00:17:13.749 line:90%
There is nothing.

00:17:22.007 --> 00:17:23.175 line:90%
More importantly,

00:17:25.010 --> 00:17:27.805 line:90%
His Majesty seems pleased
about the Prince Yeongan matter.

00:17:28.639 --> 00:17:29.849 line:90%
That is a relief.

00:17:29.932 --> 00:17:31.559 line:90%
Relief? Hardly.

00:17:32.393 --> 00:17:34.478 line:90%
If the pond spirit appears again,

00:17:35.062 --> 00:17:37.606 line:90%
Prince Yeongan will surely die.

00:17:43.445 --> 00:17:45.823 line:90%
Please get through this.

00:17:47.616 --> 00:17:48.659 line:90%
Give it to me.

00:17:50.953 --> 00:17:52.621 line:90%
Please come to your senses.

00:18:02.423 --> 00:18:06.719 line:90%
Your Majesty, Prince Yeongan,
the last remaining, lies so ill.

00:18:06.802 --> 00:18:09.847 line:90%
I truly fear for the royal succession.

00:18:10.347 --> 00:18:12.474 line:90%
Uncanny, ceaseless calamities
in the East Palace

00:18:12.558 --> 00:18:15.769 line:90%
are shaking the very foundation
of this nation.

00:18:15.853 --> 00:18:19.023 line:90%
The foundations of the nation are shaken?

00:18:19.106 --> 00:18:21.275 line:90%
Watch your tongues.

00:18:21.358 --> 00:18:23.235 line:90%
So long as I draw breath,

00:18:23.736 --> 00:18:27.239 line:90%
the foundations of this nation
will not be shaken.

00:18:28.115 --> 00:18:31.619 line:90%
Your Majesty, Prince Iksang has arrived.

00:18:34.371 --> 00:18:37.374 line:90%
-Why is Prince Iksang…
-Greetings.

00:18:37.458 --> 00:18:39.627 line:90%
Have you had your meal?

00:18:42.379 --> 00:18:44.965 line:90%
You look even younger, Aunt.

00:18:46.467 --> 00:18:49.887 line:90%
You still address me that way,
Prince Iksang.

00:18:51.221 --> 00:18:53.140 line:90%
So, how have you been?

00:18:53.641 --> 00:18:55.976 line:90%
I went on a tiger hunt in Hobyeong Valley.

00:18:56.060 --> 00:18:58.938 line:90%
I enjoyed some leisure
in Hwayang Valley as well.

00:19:00.189 --> 00:19:03.609 line:90%
Your Majesty, you should not stay
confined to the palace.

00:19:03.692 --> 00:19:06.862 line:90%
Some rest beyond its walls
would serve you well.

00:19:07.446 --> 00:19:09.073 line:90%
I am not sure.

00:19:10.324 --> 00:19:12.534 line:90%
I entered here as Crown Princess
at the age of 11

00:19:12.618 --> 00:19:15.412 line:90%
and have never set foot beyond the walls.

00:19:16.455 --> 00:19:20.209 line:90%
This palace is where I am to remain
until the day I die.

00:19:22.252 --> 00:19:23.671 line:90%
You remain unchanged.

00:19:23.754 --> 00:19:25.923 line:90%
But why did you wish to see me?

00:19:31.136 --> 00:19:32.888 line:90%
How is your son doing?

00:19:42.564 --> 00:19:44.483 line:90%
He is doing well.

00:19:46.694 --> 00:19:50.114 line:90%
Unlike me,
he delights in scholarly pursuits.

00:19:50.197 --> 00:19:55.285 line:90%
After all, royal relatives are barred
from holding office.

00:19:56.036 --> 00:20:01.583 line:90%
A small stream cannot travel far
once it leaves the main flow.

00:20:02.084 --> 00:20:07.172 line:90%
But if the main river
turns foul and runs dry…

00:20:10.509 --> 00:20:14.388 line:90%
we should cut it off
and open a new channel, should we not?

00:20:15.764 --> 00:20:17.516 line:90%
<i>How dare a mere feng shui master</i>

00:20:17.599 --> 00:20:20.561 line:90%
seek an audience
with Her Majesty so easily.

00:20:21.228 --> 00:20:22.187 line:90%
Leave at once.

00:20:22.688 --> 00:20:25.399 line:90%
He entered the palace
on His Majesty's command.

00:20:25.482 --> 00:20:27.860 line:90%
He has something to report to Her Majesty.

00:20:29.278 --> 00:20:30.988 line:90%
It is also the will of His Majesty.

00:20:32.823 --> 00:20:33.949 line:90%
Wait here.

00:20:41.707 --> 00:20:44.126 line:90%
She is damn prickly.

00:20:46.795 --> 00:20:48.964 line:90%
She is the highest elder
of the Internal Court.

00:20:49.465 --> 00:20:51.675 line:90%
Do you think an audience
is easily granted?

00:21:00.309 --> 00:21:01.685 line:90%
I hear a strange noise.

00:21:18.911 --> 00:21:20.954 line:90%
This damn Yin energy in the palace…

00:21:39.181 --> 00:21:40.724 line:90%
Her Majesty is occupied.

00:21:40.808 --> 00:21:42.309 line:90%
You may withdraw.

00:21:46.063 --> 00:21:48.315 line:90%
Goodness, what a shame.

00:21:48.816 --> 00:21:51.485 line:90%
I had something to report
about the pond spirit.

00:21:51.568 --> 00:21:54.238 line:90%
What did you say? The pond spirit?

00:21:56.615 --> 00:21:58.659 line:90%
Then please deliver this message.

00:22:01.995 --> 00:22:03.831 line:90%
Once Prince Yeongan is dead,

00:22:04.331 --> 00:22:07.209 line:90%
Her Majesty should consider
who comes next.

00:22:08.168 --> 00:22:09.128 line:90%
What?

00:22:09.670 --> 00:22:10.504 line:90%
Next?

00:22:15.676 --> 00:22:17.761 line:90%
What do you…

00:22:24.935 --> 00:22:26.645 line:90%
This was a wasted trip.

00:22:28.605 --> 00:22:31.900 line:90%
-Meeting the Queen Dowager at all--
-No, there is a gain.

00:22:32.442 --> 00:22:33.986 line:90%
A gain? What do you mean?

00:22:35.070 --> 00:22:36.947 line:90%
Wait. You are…

00:22:46.874 --> 00:22:48.500 line:90%
She lives in a private residence.

00:22:49.126 --> 00:22:50.836 line:90%
Why is she here in the palace?

00:22:54.339 --> 00:22:56.425 line:90%
Who is that? Do you know each other?

00:22:56.925 --> 00:23:01.138 line:90%
She is my grandmother
and the birth mother of His Majesty.

00:23:06.435 --> 00:23:09.605 line:90%
Is that why the Queen Dowager
and the King are at odds?

00:23:09.688 --> 00:23:11.565 line:90%
Because they are not related by blood?

00:23:13.734 --> 00:23:18.238 line:90%
More likely, His Majesty was born
to a court lady who became a concubine.

00:23:21.491 --> 00:23:22.993 line:90%
<i>Thirty years ago,</i>

00:23:23.994 --> 00:23:28.957 line:90%
<i>all of my father's brothers died</i>
<i>for unknown reasons.</i>

00:23:30.959 --> 00:23:34.338 line:90%
<i>He was the only surviving son</i>
<i>of the late King and became Crown Prince,</i>

00:23:34.838 --> 00:23:37.549 line:90%
<i>but Her Majesty did not recognize him</i>

00:23:38.133 --> 00:23:40.177 line:90%
<i>due to the lowborn blood in his veins.</i>

00:23:42.262 --> 00:23:44.932 line:90%
<i>Even now, after he became King.</i>

00:23:57.569 --> 00:23:58.528 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:23:59.029 --> 00:24:03.450 line:90%
For the nation and its people,
you must appoint a new Crown Prince.

00:24:03.951 --> 00:24:05.535 line:90%
I am aware of this.

00:24:06.036 --> 00:24:10.123 line:90%
But Prince Yeongan has yet to recover.

00:24:10.207 --> 00:24:12.626 line:90%
That is precisely why we say this.

00:24:12.709 --> 00:24:15.837 line:90%
Your Majesty, measures must be taken.

00:24:17.547 --> 00:24:18.674 line:90%
What measures?

00:24:19.174 --> 00:24:25.055 line:90%
You must select one of the royal kin
and name him Crown Prince.

00:24:25.973 --> 00:24:27.891 line:90%
Please grant your approval.

00:24:28.392 --> 00:24:31.520 line:90%
-Please grant your approval.
-Please grant your approval.

00:24:33.855 --> 00:24:37.109 line:90%
Are you of the belief

00:24:38.902 --> 00:24:40.320 line:90%
that my son will die?

00:24:41.822 --> 00:24:44.241 line:90%
How could we harbor
such irreverent thoughts…

00:24:44.741 --> 00:24:46.952 line:90%
That is not what we intend.

00:24:47.035 --> 00:24:48.328 line:90%
You did not intend it?!

00:24:50.163 --> 00:24:51.707 line:90%
Then whose intention is it?

00:24:55.585 --> 00:24:57.629 line:90%
The Queen Dowager?

00:25:01.091 --> 00:25:04.011 line:90%
I am deeply disappointed in you.

00:25:05.137 --> 00:25:07.639 line:90%
I went to great lengths
to bring you into the palace,

00:25:08.223 --> 00:25:12.102 line:90%
yet you failed to control even one spirit
and instead cured Prince Yeongan.

00:25:13.020 --> 00:25:15.731 line:90%
I did not drive the spirit out.

00:25:16.773 --> 00:25:19.860 line:90%
I meant to draw it to Prince Yeongan.

00:25:19.943 --> 00:25:22.571 line:90%
Then was there someone who drove it out?

00:25:23.071 --> 00:25:25.782 line:90%
The feng shui master the King brought in
seems suspicious.

00:25:25.866 --> 00:25:28.660 line:90%
What? The feng shui master
the King brought in?

00:25:37.377 --> 00:25:39.838 line:90%
Keep a close eye on him.

00:25:40.839 --> 00:25:43.300 line:90%
If he truly has the power
to get rid of spirits…

00:25:45.886 --> 00:25:47.346 line:90%
we must kill him.

00:25:48.722 --> 00:25:52.100 line:90%
As the spirits run rampant in the palace,
the King is driven into a corner,

00:25:52.684 --> 00:25:54.311 line:90%
and that serves me well.

00:25:55.854 --> 00:25:58.398 line:90%
Prince Iksang was
at the Queen Dowager's residence?

00:26:02.527 --> 00:26:05.197 line:90%
Truly impressive.

00:26:13.789 --> 00:26:17.876 line:90%
So she intends to change
the royal bloodline?

00:26:19.378 --> 00:26:23.632 line:90%
<i>She means to break the curse</i>
<i>that began 30 years ago</i>

00:26:24.216 --> 00:26:26.968 line:90%
<i>and start anew.</i>

00:26:28.595 --> 00:26:30.764 line:90%
<i>Yet it will not be easy.</i>

00:26:33.517 --> 00:26:37.437 line:90%
<i>And bound by sin,</i>

00:26:37.938 --> 00:26:41.149 line:90%
<i>how could she flee on her own?</i>

00:27:13.598 --> 00:27:14.599 line:90%
Look here.

00:27:16.184 --> 00:27:17.102 line:90%
Look!

00:27:17.185 --> 00:27:18.895 line:90%
Wait. What is wrong with you?

00:27:23.984 --> 00:27:25.652 line:90%
Who are you again?

00:27:25.735 --> 00:27:27.737 line:90%
I am Ji-yul,
an apprentice from Saenggwabang.

00:27:28.238 --> 00:27:30.866 line:90%
Starting today, I will be sharing
this chamber with you.

00:27:30.949 --> 00:27:32.701 line:90%
What? That cannot be.

00:27:32.784 --> 00:27:33.702 line:90%
There we go.

00:27:34.327 --> 00:27:35.162 line:90%
Look.

00:27:35.787 --> 00:27:38.623 line:90%
I was told I would have my own chamber.

00:27:38.707 --> 00:27:41.168 line:90%
I have never shared one
with anyone before.

00:27:41.251 --> 00:27:43.295 line:90%
This must be uncomfortable for you.

00:27:43.378 --> 00:27:44.796 line:90%
Not at all.

00:27:45.297 --> 00:27:46.756 line:90%
Before I came to the palace,

00:27:47.340 --> 00:27:49.634 line:90%
my family of nine shared a room.

00:27:51.428 --> 00:27:52.387 line:90%
I see.

00:27:56.349 --> 00:27:57.476 line:90%
The spirit…

00:27:58.643 --> 00:28:00.896 line:90%
Why is it so noisy out there?

00:28:00.979 --> 00:28:03.773 line:90%
What? Oh my! Have you not heard?

00:28:03.857 --> 00:28:06.485 line:90%
A spirit appeared
in the Queen Dowager's residence.

00:28:06.568 --> 00:28:08.236 line:90%
-The Queen Dowager's residence?
-Yes.

00:28:08.320 --> 00:28:11.406 line:90%
Ever since I came to the palace,
the spirit incidents keep happening.

00:28:11.490 --> 00:28:14.075 line:90%
-It appeared in Saenggwabang as well--
-Wait.

00:28:14.868 --> 00:28:17.329 line:90%
More about the spirit
in the Queen Dowager's residence.

00:28:18.288 --> 00:28:20.123 line:90%
Good grief, it is cold.

00:28:37.849 --> 00:28:38.850 line:90%
Damn it.

00:28:40.977 --> 00:28:41.811 line:90%
What the…

00:28:42.395 --> 00:28:43.855 line:90%
When did you get in here?

00:28:46.566 --> 00:28:47.442 line:90%
Stop.

00:28:48.860 --> 00:28:49.861 line:90%
You.

00:28:50.820 --> 00:28:52.280 line:90%
Who said you could act cute?

00:28:53.657 --> 00:28:56.034 line:90%
Why me of all people? Why?

00:28:56.117 --> 00:28:57.786 line:90%
Why? Damn it…

00:28:59.287 --> 00:29:02.123 line:90%
The salt storehouse spirit is
in the Queen Dowager's residence.

00:29:03.416 --> 00:29:05.085 line:90%
-The Queen Dowager?
-Let us go.

00:29:05.168 --> 00:29:06.962 line:90%
We must look into the salt storehouse.

00:29:07.546 --> 00:29:10.173 line:90%
Very well.
I want to get out of here as well.

00:29:10.799 --> 00:29:11.967 line:90%
What?

00:29:35.407 --> 00:29:36.449 line:90%
Can you hear anything?

00:29:38.368 --> 00:29:39.703 line:90%
What are they saying?

00:29:41.037 --> 00:29:44.124 line:90%
I cannot make out what they are saying.
Their voices are too low.

00:29:51.214 --> 00:29:52.799 line:90%
I need to go inside.

00:30:04.060 --> 00:30:05.895 line:90%
Must you go in alone?

00:30:11.151 --> 00:30:12.277 line:90%
I will be fine.

00:30:12.777 --> 00:30:15.030 line:90%
Then I will wait here.

00:31:11.127 --> 00:31:12.462 line:90%
Tell me.

00:31:13.546 --> 00:31:15.382 line:90%
What do you wish to say?

00:31:21.262 --> 00:31:22.931 line:90%
Please clear our names.

00:31:25.100 --> 00:31:26.184 line:90%
So unjust…

00:31:41.950 --> 00:31:43.410 line:90%
The serpent's cast skin

00:31:43.910 --> 00:31:46.496 line:90%
killed the dragon's child.

00:31:46.996 --> 00:31:50.917 line:90%
<i>"The serpent's cast skin</i>
<i>killed the dragon's child."</i>

00:31:51.000 --> 00:31:53.878 line:90%
Tell me who wrote these words.

00:31:55.213 --> 00:31:58.967 line:90%
The dragon's child
refers to the late Crown Prince.

00:31:59.634 --> 00:32:02.303 line:90%
Her Majesty the Queen
was born in the Year of the Snake.

00:32:02.804 --> 00:32:07.267 line:90%
This means the Crown Prince died
because of Her Majesty.

00:32:08.268 --> 00:32:12.063 line:90%
One of you must have defiled
the royal house.

00:32:14.065 --> 00:32:16.359 line:90%
You will be confined and starved
until you confess.

00:32:16.443 --> 00:32:18.653 line:90%
You will not be given a drop of water!

00:32:40.300 --> 00:32:43.344 line:90%
Please save us!

00:32:46.389 --> 00:32:48.391 line:90%
Please save us!

00:32:50.393 --> 00:32:51.644 line:90%
Please!

00:33:01.488 --> 00:33:03.364 line:90%
They were burned to death?

00:33:07.452 --> 00:33:10.413 line:90%
Place the bones of the dead court ladies
in jars and bury them.

00:33:11.122 --> 00:33:14.793 line:90%
Their resentment must be sealed
so it cannot harm the royal house.

00:33:14.876 --> 00:33:15.794 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:33:34.729 --> 00:33:39.776 line:90%
Have you looked into
who broke the sealed jars?

00:33:40.777 --> 00:33:42.237 line:90%
I looked into it

00:33:42.737 --> 00:33:46.074 line:90%
but could not find anyone
who entered the salt storehouse.

00:33:48.576 --> 00:33:50.912 line:90%
This must have been done

00:33:51.454 --> 00:33:53.748 line:90%
by someone who knows
exactly what the jars contain.

00:33:54.874 --> 00:33:58.294 line:90%
But we alone know of those jars.

00:33:59.587 --> 00:34:02.006 line:90%
This must be aimed at me.

00:34:02.090 --> 00:34:03.258 line:90%
Who could it be…

00:34:06.594 --> 00:34:07.595 line:90%
Yes.

00:34:08.721 --> 00:34:10.807 line:90%
There is one more person.

00:34:11.516 --> 00:34:12.892 line:90%
Who is it?

00:34:14.310 --> 00:34:18.439 line:90%
I must have been blinded
by fear of the spirit for a moment.

00:34:18.523 --> 00:34:20.775 line:90%
Why did I not see it sooner?

00:34:21.359 --> 00:34:24.529 line:90%
<i>The trouble began</i>
<i>after I met Prince Iksang.</i>

00:34:24.612 --> 00:34:26.739 line:90%
He has pulled through.

00:34:26.823 --> 00:34:31.369 line:90%
I believe it is time
to appoint a Crown Prince.

00:34:31.452 --> 00:34:34.706 line:90%
<i>His Majesty saw right through me!</i>

00:34:35.248 --> 00:34:37.500 line:90%
He is trying to stop me.

00:34:37.584 --> 00:34:40.211 line:90%
He means to use the spirit against me.

00:34:40.295 --> 00:34:43.506 line:90%
His Majesty wants me to die tonight!

00:34:48.011 --> 00:34:50.179 line:90%
<i>But I will not allow that to happen.</i>

00:34:50.263 --> 00:34:53.224 line:90%
<i>I will not die to a mere spirit.</i>

00:34:54.267 --> 00:34:55.768 line:90%
Night will soon fall.

00:34:55.852 --> 00:34:57.770 line:90%
Court ladies, do not sleep.

00:34:57.854 --> 00:35:01.065 line:90%
Protect me from the spirit!

00:35:02.317 --> 00:35:03.276 line:90%
<i>So,</i>

00:35:03.359 --> 00:35:04.694 line:90%
for 30 years,

00:35:04.777 --> 00:35:08.156 line:90%
the pond spirit has been killing
the princes of the East Palace,

00:35:08.948 --> 00:35:13.536 line:90%
and the court ladies claimed the princes
were dying because of the Queen Dowager?

00:35:14.037 --> 00:35:17.874 line:90%
It was not the court ladies.
They were falsely accused and killed.

00:35:19.083 --> 00:35:22.795 line:90%
What is certain is that the Queen Dowager
is connected to the pond spirit.

00:35:24.839 --> 00:35:26.341 line:90%
Yet, thanks to your ability,

00:35:26.424 --> 00:35:29.052 line:90%
I now understand why the court ladies
became won-gwi.

00:35:30.345 --> 00:35:32.263 line:90%
I could not have done it alone.

00:35:33.431 --> 00:35:34.557 line:90%
You did well.

00:35:37.143 --> 00:35:38.353 line:90%
You are the first

00:35:39.479 --> 00:35:41.814 line:90%
to find this strange ability useful.

00:35:42.315 --> 00:35:43.316 line:90%
Is that so?

00:35:43.399 --> 00:35:46.903 line:90%
I thought His Majesty sent you to me
because he valued your ability.

00:35:46.986 --> 00:35:49.989 line:90%
I suppose I was of some use
in dealing with spirits.

00:35:55.411 --> 00:35:56.746 line:90%
You on bad terms with your father?

00:36:01.501 --> 00:36:03.169 line:90%
Hold your tongue.

00:36:03.252 --> 00:36:09.008 line:90%
Do not say
that my own child hears such things.

00:36:09.550 --> 00:36:12.095 line:90%
Unless you mean to disgrace
the royal house.

00:36:13.972 --> 00:36:18.768 line:90%
One born of the royal blood who hears
strange things would be a disgrace.

00:36:22.981 --> 00:36:23.815 line:90%
Good.

00:36:27.110 --> 00:36:28.486 line:90%
What do you mean?

00:36:30.154 --> 00:36:30.989 line:90%
I mean,

00:36:31.864 --> 00:36:33.574 line:90%
since we both dislike His Majesty,

00:36:33.658 --> 00:36:35.827 line:90%
it suddenly feels like
we are on the same side.

00:36:38.454 --> 00:36:40.123 line:90%
More importantly,

00:36:41.749 --> 00:36:44.502 line:90%
when I heard the cries
from the salt storehouse back then,

00:36:45.003 --> 00:36:46.254 line:90%
I should have helped.

00:36:47.922 --> 00:36:50.466 line:90%
If only I had broken the jars
that held their souls…

00:36:50.967 --> 00:36:53.428 line:90%
What could a mere child have done?

00:36:53.928 --> 00:36:56.514 line:90%
It must have been hard
to bear that strange gift.

00:36:57.640 --> 00:36:59.392 line:90%
Do not blame yourself.

00:37:05.106 --> 00:37:09.360 line:90%
I, too, was feared and pointed at.

00:37:10.361 --> 00:37:12.822 line:90%
You can simply ignore such people.

00:37:16.659 --> 00:37:19.620 line:90%
Just beware of the spirits

00:37:19.704 --> 00:37:21.956 line:90%
so you do not end up getting possessed.

00:37:29.297 --> 00:37:30.339 line:90%
Now I understand

00:37:31.049 --> 00:37:32.592 line:90%
why you are so peculiar.

00:37:33.384 --> 00:37:34.218 line:90%
Me?

00:37:35.720 --> 00:37:37.764 line:90%
I will lay the bones to rest.

00:37:37.847 --> 00:37:39.807 line:90%
Look. Hold on.

00:37:39.891 --> 00:37:42.977 line:90%
What? I will have these bones
of the court ladies ground to powder.

00:37:43.478 --> 00:37:44.479 line:90%
What?

00:37:45.980 --> 00:37:47.440 line:90%
Ground to powder?

00:37:48.608 --> 00:37:49.942 line:90%
No, you must not!

00:37:50.943 --> 00:37:54.280 line:90%
-Do you mean to dishonor the dead again?
-Good grief.

00:37:54.781 --> 00:37:56.824 line:90%
I am tired of explaining it every time.

00:37:57.325 --> 00:38:00.828 line:90%
Won-gwi is a spirit that cannot pass on

00:38:00.912 --> 00:38:02.955 line:90%
because it carries resentment.

00:38:03.581 --> 00:38:06.584 line:90%
So if you use things
that remind it of who it once was

00:38:06.667 --> 00:38:08.544 line:90%
and dissolve that mass of resentment…

00:38:10.630 --> 00:38:12.298 line:90%
you may send it to the afterlife.

00:38:13.007 --> 00:38:15.843 line:90%
Then those souls will not disappear,
will they?

00:38:15.927 --> 00:38:17.095 line:90%
They are pitiful souls.

00:38:17.178 --> 00:38:19.472 line:90%
Pitiful or not,

00:38:19.555 --> 00:38:22.600 line:90%
they are harming innocent people.

00:38:23.226 --> 00:38:25.394 line:90%
-We have no time.
-What do you mean?

00:38:25.478 --> 00:38:27.897 line:90%
Are you telling me
that spirits will appear again?

00:38:31.109 --> 00:38:33.694 line:90%
It must be right
by the Queen Dowager already.

00:39:00.930 --> 00:39:02.849 line:90%
Is there no one outside?

00:39:03.850 --> 00:39:06.018 line:90%
Bring me a candle.

00:39:31.210 --> 00:39:36.215 line:90%
<i>You should take these ashes to the shrine</i>
<i>where the Queen Dowager is.</i>

00:39:37.717 --> 00:39:41.971 line:90%
<i>I will go into the Realm of Gwi</i>
<i>and seek the spirits out.</i>

00:39:44.974 --> 00:39:46.726 line:90%
<i>They should be right beside</i>
<i>the Queen Dowager.</i>

00:40:14.212 --> 00:40:15.838 line:90%
I am sorry.

00:40:47.286 --> 00:40:50.331 line:90%
<i>As you said, they are innocent won-gwi.</i>

00:40:53.125 --> 00:40:56.045 line:90%
<i>To release their grudge,</i>
<i>we must destroy that mass of resentment.</i>

00:40:58.631 --> 00:41:01.842 line:90%
<i>Begin when I ring the bell.</i>

00:42:57.333 --> 00:42:59.543 line:90%
<i>Is this the only way?</i>

00:43:03.339 --> 00:43:05.591 line:90%
At this rate, I will be the one to die.

00:43:33.160 --> 00:43:34.495 line:90%
Hurry!

00:43:34.995 --> 00:43:36.414 line:90%
Quick!

00:44:14.410 --> 00:44:15.911 line:90%
<i>Let go of your grievances…</i>

00:44:18.622 --> 00:44:20.541 line:90%
<i>release your anger</i>…

00:44:23.711 --> 00:44:26.088 line:90%
<i>and rest in peace.</i>

00:44:30.176 --> 00:44:32.386 line:90%
<i>I will send you to the afterlife.</i>

00:44:33.929 --> 00:44:35.431 line:90%
<i>May you all</i>…

00:44:38.225 --> 00:44:40.978 line:90%
<i>be reborn in paradise.</i>

00:45:11.258 --> 00:45:14.595 line:90%
We were wronged.

00:45:14.678 --> 00:45:17.515 line:90%
This is unjust.

00:45:19.391 --> 00:45:22.228 line:90%
We were wronged.

00:45:23.729 --> 00:45:25.856 line:90%
This is unjust.

00:45:26.565 --> 00:45:29.902 line:90%
-What you did to my mother and me…
-We were wronged.

00:45:29.985 --> 00:45:31.612 line:90%
I have not forgotten at all.

00:45:32.112 --> 00:45:37.284 line:90%
This is most… unjust.

00:45:37.785 --> 00:45:40.246 line:90%
What is it that you find unjust?

00:45:46.210 --> 00:45:47.753 line:90%
Our only sin

00:45:49.296 --> 00:45:52.550 line:90%
was being there.

00:45:53.050 --> 00:45:53.884 line:90%
Who…

00:45:54.927 --> 00:45:56.428 line:90%
Who are you?

00:45:59.223 --> 00:46:04.144 line:90%
When the Most Favored Lady of the Court
uttered a curse as she died…

00:46:09.733 --> 00:46:14.280 line:90%
No royal blood shall flow
in this palace any longer.

00:46:14.363 --> 00:46:17.157 line:90%
You insolent wench, how dare you!

00:46:17.241 --> 00:46:19.868 line:90%
I will die, become a spirit,

00:46:20.494 --> 00:46:23.330 line:90%
and sever the royal bloodline.

00:46:24.039 --> 00:46:26.125 line:90%
I will eradicate the royal bloodline

00:46:26.208 --> 00:46:29.753 line:90%
and wipe out every last seed
of the East Palace!

00:46:31.005 --> 00:46:32.256 line:90%
What are you waiting for?

00:46:43.058 --> 00:46:46.770 line:90%
<i>"No royal blood shall flow</i>
<i>in this palace any longer."</i>

00:46:47.813 --> 00:46:50.316 line:90%
<i>"I will wipe out every last seed</i>
<i>of the East Palace."</i>

00:46:50.816 --> 00:46:55.362 line:90%
<i>She killed us for hearing the curse</i>
<i>of the Most Favored Lady of the Court.</i>

00:46:57.448 --> 00:47:00.784 line:90%
<i>"The serpent's cast skin</i>
<i>killed the dragon's child."</i>

00:47:01.910 --> 00:47:06.290 line:90%
<i>Using the writing on the wall</i>
<i>as an excuse!</i>

00:47:11.962 --> 00:47:13.589 line:90%
The Most Favored Lady of the Court?

00:47:17.760 --> 00:47:21.930 line:90%
Then the pond spirit is
the Most Favored Lady of the Court?

00:47:23.974 --> 00:47:27.603 line:90%
We were wronged.

00:47:29.647 --> 00:47:32.566 line:90%
While we were dying,

00:47:33.359 --> 00:47:37.696 line:90%
why did you just stand by?

00:47:39.198 --> 00:47:43.577 line:90%
<i>Those who sin are punished eventually.</i>

00:47:46.914 --> 00:47:49.416 line:90%
<i>You need not take a life.</i>

00:50:50.222 --> 00:50:53.559 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang